## Changelog from v1

- All 5 design decisions integrated into the relevant tasks
- P1.1 expanded with explicit file-by-file migration checklist; "no fallback" constraint added
- P1.2 reflects decision to skip code signing; SmartScreen workflow documented
- P1.3 makes default-block + override checkbox explicit
- P2.1 wires the cancelled-status DB write into the cancel flow
- P3.1 makes `history_max_runs` a config.yaml variable
- P2.2 in v1 (per-cluster selection) renumbered to P3.4 because of dependency on P3.1
- P2.3 in v1 (bug carry-overs) renumbered to P2.2
- P3.4 quick actions now include "Select cancelled clusters from last run" (leveraging the cancel-status data)

